Class Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • Type
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanType, IntegerType, Quantity, RealType, StringType

    public abstract class Type
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class for a specific primitive type. It has a name and can be numeric or not.
